%set(name,tolower
)%set(syntax,%%tolower(str)
)%set(description,Transform str to uppercase\, %%toupper()\, or all lowercase\, %%tolower().

Only alphabetic characters are affected by this macro. The current language 
defined by the operating system is used to transform extended characters (such 
as ones with accents).
)%set(author,
)%set(example,
)%set(seealso,
)
	 tolower  
 